<p class="artwork">The Dance</p>
<p class="artist">John Leech</p>
<p class="size">12 x 7 cm, vignetted</p>
<p class="artdate">1845</p>
<p class="medium">Wood engraving</p>
<p class="place">Full-page illustration for Dickens's <span class="book">The Cricket on 
the Hearth</span>: "Chirp the Third," 172.</p> 

