<h3>Illustrations for the Third Volume of the Pears' Centenary <span 
class="h3book">Christmas Books</span> of Charles Dickens (1912)</h3> 
<p class="lq">Each contains about thirty illustrations from original drawings by Charles 
Green, R. I.  — Clement Shorter (1912)</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="cricket.html">L. Rossi's <span class="book">The Cricket on the Hearth</span> 
(22 plates)</a></li>
</ul>

